text=The pages below describe various aspects of using and administering a PmWiki installation.  As you can see, the documentation is still incomplete.  If you have suggestions, additions, or improvements for the documentation, please contribute them to pmichaud.com's PmWiki:DocumentationIndex page so they can be incorporated into future distributions of PmWiki!께* Beginner topics for creating and editing pages in PmWiki** {{WikiWord}}s** BasicEditing** CreatingNewPages** LinksToExternalPages** ImagesInWikiPages** FreeLinks** DeletePages** TipsForEditing* Intermediate editing topics** TextFormattingRules - convenient one-page-stop for many common markups** WikiStyles - colored text, links in new windows** InterMap links - URI[=/=]URL shortcuts** SpecialMarkups - specialized markups (double-brackets)** SimpleTables ** SimpleTablesII** AdvancedTables** {{Uploads}} - upload and attach files to pages* {{WikiStructure}}s - organizing and protecting pages in PmWiki** {{WikiGroup}}s - organize pages into groups** {{Passwords}} - password protect pages and groups** WikiTrails - create paths (trails) through PmWiki pages** GroupHeaders - add content to the beginning of all pages in a WikiGroup  (Refers to [=GroupFooters=] too!)** PageRevisions - view/recover previous versions of a page* [=PmWiki=] site administration ** SystemRequirements** {{Installation}} - downloading and installing PmWiki** InitialSetupTasks - initial customizations, the @@local.php@@ file** LocalCustomizations - details about customizing PmWiki*** ChangePmWikiURL - change the URI[=/=]URL used to access PmWiki*** CustomHeadersAndFooters - change the headers and footers*** PerGroupCustomizations - per-group or per-page customizations*** {{CustomInterMap}}s - add custom InterMap links*** {{Robots}} - prevent search engines from indexing PmWiki-command pages*** PasswordsAdmin - set site-wide and admin passwords*** UploadsAdmin - configure the upload.php module*** MailPosts - send mail whenever pages are updated*** WikiStylesAdmin - customize available WikiStyles*** CustomFreeLinks - customizing free link display*** CustomMarkup** {{Upgrades}} - upgrade to new PmWiki releases** EditQuickReference - text that appears beneath the Edit Page form** UploadQuickReference - text that appears on the {{Uploads}} form** FilesAndDirectories** {{Variables}}** PageLayout** AvailableActions ** TroubleShooting** UninstallingPmWiki * About PmWiki** PmWikiPhilosophy - design principles behind PmWiki** PmWiki.{{Audiences}} - who PmWiki is designed for** PmWiki.{{Contributors}} - people who have helped make PmWiki great** PmWiki.{{Size}}
